---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const title = 'FUSA Damascus · Selected work · Rekraft Design';
const description = 'FUSA Damascus forged the ultimate chef knife. We built the digital experience to match: cinematic, single-product, made for cooks. Case study by Rekraft Design.';
const canonical = 'https://rekraft.design/work/fusa-kitchen';
---

<Base title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <Nav />
  <main class="case">
    <div class="frame case-back-wrap">
      <a href="/#work" class="case-back font-mono">&larr; Selected Work</a>
    </div>

    <section class="section case-intro">
      <div class="frame">
        <header class="case-head">
          <span class="eyebrow">Case Study &middot; 02 &middot; Knives</span>
          <h1 class="display-1 reveal-words" data-hero-headline>
            FUSA Damascus. <em class="italic-accent">The one knife.</em>
          </h1>
          <p class="lead fade-up">
            FUSA crafted a physical masterclass in high-carbon steel. We built an editorial commerce experience that <em class="italic-accent">makes you feel the edge.</em>
          </p>
          <a href="https://fusa-kitchen.vercel.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary case-cta-link fade-up">
            Visit the live site <span class="case-arrow-up">&#8599;</span>
          </a>
        </header>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="case-meta-strip">
      <div class="frame case-meta-inner font-mono">
        <span><b>Industry</b> &middot; Premium kitchen goods</span>
        <span><b>Location</b> &middot; London</span>
        <span><b>Scope</b> &middot; Brand + website</span>
        <span><b>Live</b> &middot; May 2026</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Opening establishing shot: the homepage hero, the brand moment. */}
    <section class="case-shot-section case-shot-section--first">
      <div class="frame">
        <figure class="case-shot fade-up">
          <img src="/images/work/fusa/hero.jpg" alt="FUSA Damascus homepage, the Kiritsuke knife centred on a deep sage panel" loading="lazy" />
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section case-block">
      <div class="frame case-text">
        <header class="case-block-head fade-up">
          <span class="eyebrow">The ambition</span>
          <h2 class="display-2 reveal-words" data-reveal-headline>
            A knife earns its price. <em class="italic-accent">The site has to earn it too.</em>
          </h2>
        </header>
        <div class="case-prose fade-up">
          <p>FUSA forged a Kiritsuke at the price point of small luxury: hand-forged, 67-layer Damascus, a knife built to last a working career. They needed a digital home that read the same way.</p>
          <p>Quiet enough to feel premium. Focused enough to stop the scroll. Brave enough to put one product at the centre of the entire site.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* The single-product editorial PDP, proof of the focus. */}
    <section class="case-shot-section">
      <div class="frame">
        <figure class="case-shot fade-up">
          <img src="/images/work/fusa/pdp.jpg" alt="The Kiritsuke product page, single-product editorial layout with the knife full-bleed below the headline" loading="lazy" />
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section case-block">
      <div class="frame case-text">
        <header class="case-block-head fade-up">
          <span class="eyebrow">The approach</span>
          <h2 class="display-2 reveal-words" data-reveal-headline>
            Sell <em class="italic-accent">one knife.</em>
          </h2>
        </header>
        <div class="case-prose fade-up">
          <p>We threw out the standard commerce playbook. No grid of products, no carousel of categories, no menu of options. The Kiritsuke is the brand.</p>
          <p>Every section serves the same singular intent: the visitor leaves wanting that knife. The other three knives wait in their own lineup, ready when the relationship is.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* The lineup page: depth on demand, never in the way. */}
    <section class="case-shot-section">
      <div class="frame">
        <figure class="case-shot fade-up">
          <img src="/images/work/fusa/lineup.jpg" alt="The collection page revealing the three secondary knives, kept off the main story until the visitor is ready" loading="lazy" />
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section case-block">
      <div class="frame case-text">
        <header class="case-block-head fade-up">
          <span class="eyebrow">The outcome</span>
          <h2 class="display-2 reveal-words" data-reveal-headline>
            Built to <em class="italic-accent">match the knife.</em>
          </h2>
        </header>
        <ol class="case-list">
          <li class="fade-up">
            <span class="case-list-num font-mono">01</span>
            <h3 class="display-3">A brand world, not a template</h3>
            <p>Every visual decision was made specifically for FUSA. The colour, the type, the rhythm of the page, the way photography sits on the screen. Visitors land on a brand they recognise on sight, not a wrapper around a product.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up">
            <span class="case-list-num font-mono">02</span>
            <h3 class="display-3">A hero that stops the scroll</h3>
            <p>The Kiritsuke rotates as you scroll, Damascus pattern catching warm light from every angle. Product photography turned into a moment of motion. The knife is the centrepiece, and visitors notice. The story, the spec, and the price all wait until you have seen the work.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up">
            <span class="case-list-num font-mono">03</span>
            <h3 class="display-3">Copy that sounds like the cook</h3>
            <p>The page speaks to the cook reading it, not the maker writing it. Less forge romance, more honest utility. Cooks read the page, recognise themselves in it, and trust the product. That is how a premium knife earns the price on the tag.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section case-stats-section">
      <div class="frame">
        <ul class="case-stats">
          <li class="fade-up">
            <span class="case-stat-k font-mono">Live now</span>
            <div class="case-stat-big font-display"><em>1</em> hero knife</div>
            <p>The Kiritsuke, anchored as the brand. Gyuto, Cleaver, and Deba live on the secondary collection page.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up" data-d="1">
            <span class="case-stat-k font-mono">Live now</span>
            <div class="case-stat-big font-display"><em>67</em> layers</div>
            <p>VG-10 core wrapped in 67 alternating layers of soft and high-carbon steel. The number stretches to 280px on desktop and counts up from zero as you scroll past.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up" data-d="2">
            <span class="case-stat-k font-mono">Live now</span>
            <div class="case-stat-big font-display"><em>0</em> distractions</div>
            <p>We removed the standard commerce bloat. Every interaction on the page serves one purpose: putting the Kiritsuke <em>in their hands.</em></p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section case-cta">
      <div class="frame">
        <div class="case-cta-inner">
          <span class="eyebrow">Next case study</span>
          <h2 class="display-2 reveal-words" data-reveal-headline>
            Want to be <em class="italic-accent">next?</em>
          </h2>
          <p class="lead fade-up">
            We take on a small number of bespoke projects each quarter. If you have something serious to build, let's talk.
          </p>
          <a href="mailto:mark@rekraft.design?subject=Project%20Enquiry" class="btn btn-primary case-cta-btn fade-up">
            Start a conversation <span class="case-arrow-up">&#8599;</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/#work" class="case-back-bottom font-mono">&larr; All selected work</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>

<style>
  /* Back link */
  .case-back-wrap { padding-top: clamp(96px, 12vw, 140px); }
  .case-back {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color .35s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .case-back:hover { color: var(--color-ink); }

  /* Hero */
  .case-intro { padding-block: clamp(32px, 4vw, 56px) clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px); }
  .case-head { display: grid; gap: 24px; max-width: 1080px; }
  .case-cta-link { justify-self: start; margin-top: 8px; }
  .case-arrow-up { display: inline-block; transition: transform .4s var(--ease-out-expo); }
  .btn:hover .case-arrow-up { transform: translate(3px, -3px); }

  /* Meta strip */
  .case-meta-strip {
    border-block: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding-block: 16px;
  }
  .case-meta-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: clamp(16px, 3vw, 36px);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
  }
  .case-meta-inner b {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-right: 4px;
  }

  /* Curated screenshot reveal — the new centrepiece pattern.
     Replaces the live-iframe-as-centrepiece. Editorial cards with subtle
     lift and soft shadow, fade-up on scroll. Natural aspect ratio per
     image (some wide, some tall) for editorial rhythm. */
  .case-shot-section {
    padding-block: clamp(48px, 6vw, 88px);
  }
  .case-shot-section--first {
    padding-top: clamp(56px, 8vw, 100px);
  }
  .case-shot {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 80px -40px rgba(20, 20, 24, 0.32);
    transition: transform .5s var(--ease-out-expo), box-shadow .5s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .case-shot:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 40px 120px -40px rgba(20, 20, 24, 0.42);
  }
  .case-shot img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  /* Editorial section blocks — text-only ambition / approach / outcome */
  .case-block {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-block: clamp(64px, 8vw, 120px);
  }
  .case-text {
    max-width: 920px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }
  .case-block-head {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
  }
  .case-block-head .eyebrow {
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
  }
  .case-block-head h2 {
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .case-prose {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
    max-width: 60ch;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    font-size: clamp(17px, 0.6vw + 14px, 20px);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* Outcome list — three numbered items */
  .case-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--color-border);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .case-list li {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 36px) 0;
    padding-left: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 40px);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
    column-gap: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px);
    row-gap: 14px;
    align-items: baseline;
    transition: background .5s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .case-list li:hover { background: var(--color-surface); }
  .case-list-num {
    grid-row: span 2;
    color: var(--color-lime);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    padding-top: 12px;
  }
  .case-list h3 { color: var(--color-ink); }
  .case-list p {
    grid-column: 2;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    font-size: clamp(15px, 0.6vw + 12px, 18px);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  /* Live-now stats */
  .case-stats-section {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-block: clamp(56px, 6vw, 88px);
  }
  .case-stats {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 40px);
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }
  .case-stats li {
    padding: clamp(24px, 3vw, 36px);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--color-card);
    transition: border-color .25s var(--ease-out-expo), transform .25s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .case-stats li:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-border-active);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .case-stat-k {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    display: block;
  }
  .case-stat-big {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 2.4vw + 16px, 44px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .case-stat-big em {
    color: var(--color-cream);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-right: 6px;
  }
  .case-stats li p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  /* Bottom CTA */
  .case-cta {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }
  .case-cta-inner {
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
    max-width: 880px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    text-align: center;
    justify-items: center;
  }
  .case-cta-inner .lead { max-width: 56ch; }
  .case-cta-btn { justify-self: center; }
  .case-back-bottom {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
    transition: color .35s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .case-back-bottom:hover { color: var(--color-ink); }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .case-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .case-list li { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 12px; padding-left: 20px; }
    .case-list-num { grid-row: auto; padding-top: 0; }
    .case-list p { grid-column: 1; }
    .case-shot { border-radius: 10px; }
  }
</style>
